  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FLS – Sci-Fi Racing, Your Way</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FLS is a fast-paced <strong>sci-fi sandbox racing</strong> game built for precision, competition, and creativity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race through challenging courses, hit every ring with accuracy, and climb the leaderboards. The scoring system rewards perfection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete <strong>solo or in multiplayer</strong>, challenging friends and players worldwide. Build and share custom tracks with the easy-to-use level editor, then test your skills on community-made courses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the speed, refine your technique, and stay ahead of the competition.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FLS – Sci-Fi Racing, Your Way</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FLS is a fast-paced <strong>sci-fi sandbox racing</strong> game built for precision, competition, and creativity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race through challenging courses, hit every ring with accuracy, and climb the leaderboards. The scoring system rewards perfection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete <strong>solo or in multiplayer</strong>, challenging friends and players worldwide. Build and share custom tracks with the easy-to-use level editor, then test your skills on community-made courses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the speed, refine your technique, and stay ahead of the competition.</p>",
